title: SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket launches 29 Starlink satellites to orbit from Florida
description: A SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket carrying 29 Starlink satellites launched from the Cape Canaveral Space Force Station in Florida on Sunday, Jan. 18, 2026.
